name: ShareFeelings
0:
”Alexa, open share feelings”
”what are you feeling”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: share feelings
des: Share Feelings is an Alexa Skill which tells the user how their Alexa is feeling right now. The concept is hypothetical and has no relation with the feelings in machines. You may found that your Alexa is feeling happy or it might be sad as well. It's just for fun.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
